{"tid":903454,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工對住呢啲同事 為乜！！！","createTime":"2018-11-15T14:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T15:41:27.000Z","uid":84691,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"418e0ce9b96f0b41acdf1266ac72f73d8dfb69f3","tid":903454,"uid":84691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:22:41.000Z","msg":"返工返到有感而發 想搵個正常同事傾下計都無<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1. 虛 偽 同 事</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日背後捅其他同事幾刀<br />\n<br />\n表面上又扮哂FD<br />\n<br />\n同呢種人共事好辛苦 都唔知佢暗地裡桶左我幾多下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>2. 講 幾 句 野 起 哂 鋼 - 唔 識 尊 重</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時好有禮貌咁教下佢野 同 交流意見（佢FG）<br />\n<br />\n點知條撚樣乜鳩都反 見我同佢講野好聲好氣<br />\n<br />\n就真係以為我同佢平起平坐 （小器都係咁話）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>3. 成日講事非</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯恐天下不亂 成日講人不是<br />\n<br />\n又唔做好自己份內事 係都要當人敵人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>4. 自己</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日日返工面對啲咁既同事 都仲要留係到<br />\n<br />\n奢望自己可以因此有所成長 <br />\n<br />\n但又唔知為乜 又無目標"},{"pid":"6aca1bee57b5220b6afe50bc8723f6acf7f741f1","tid":903454,"uid":184725,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"418e0ce9b96f0b41acdf1266ac72f73d8dfb69f3","tid":903454,"uid":84691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:22:41.000Z","msg":"返工返到有感而發 想搵個正常同事傾下計都無<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1. 虛 偽 同 事</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日背後捅其他同事幾刀<br />\n<br />\n表面上又扮哂FD<br />\n<br />\n同呢種人共事好辛苦 都唔知佢暗地裡桶左我幾多下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>2. 講 幾 句 野 起 哂 鋼 - 唔 識 尊 重</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時好有禮貌咁教下佢野 同 交流意見（佢FG）<br />\n<br />\n點知條撚樣乜鳩都反 見我同佢講野好聲好氣<br />\n<br />\n就真係以為我同佢平起平坐 （小器都係咁話）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>3. 成日講事非</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯恐天下不亂 成日講人不是<br />\n<br />\n又唔做好自己份內事 係都要當人敵人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>4. 自己</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日日返工面對啲咁既同事 都仲要留係到<br />\n<br />\n奢望自己可以因此有所成長 <br />\n<br />\n但又唔知為乜 又無目標"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"返學都有呢d人！<br />\n只不過果陣可以揀人黎識。<br />\n但工作上，你要焗住同不同性格嘅人相處。<br />\n無得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n命運安排咗你同佢地共事都無辦法，<br />\n唯有當學嘢！返工搵錢係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都學習緊～"},{"pid":"4f357b65c20b0384769e2349e8a3c60467a13590","tid":903454,"uid":108816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"做邊行"},{"pid":"7786f2657a1f1493382e1a4563a9c4627709a69f","tid":903454,"uid":84691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"想識個相似價值觀既同事真難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd905def0fbeac87588077ef5c0128cbbdadafc2","tid":903454,"uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"老油條+閪女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主真係唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bf0f4ca191d7a0f9f14d2f8c8f7bb56272518a","tid":903454,"uid":192327,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"418e0ce9b96f0b41acdf1266ac72f73d8dfb69f3","tid":903454,"uid":84691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T14:22:41.000Z","msg":"返工返到有感而發 想搵個正常同事傾下計都無<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1. 虛 偽 同 事</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日背後捅其他同事幾刀<br />\n<br />\n表面上又扮哂FD<br />\n<br />\n同呢種人共事好辛苦 都唔知佢暗地裡桶左我幾多下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>2. 講 幾 句 野 起 哂 鋼 - 唔 識 尊 重</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/